# 📅 Day 6 – HAVING Clause

## Topics Covered

- HAVING

## Brief Explanation

`WHERE` filters rows before grouping.

`HAVING` filters groups after aggregation.

### Example

```sql
SELECT department,
AVG(salary)
FROM Employees
GROUP BY department
HAVING AVG(salary) > 50000;
```

### Practiced Problems

- Find Team with Highest Average Rating
- User with Highest Rating in Each College

